{
  "stem": "25651.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Another man comes in, and he's got hernia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now, they finished this operation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I still feel sort of, you know, sleepy and-- you don't feel well after you've collapsed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In Yiddish you say it's tsemisht, which is a lovely word, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] 'Tsemisht' means mixed up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You're all mixed up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And They bring this man in, and he's got his sack between his legs right down to his knees like this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Hernia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And this Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Heller-- as it happens, also Dr-- a Heller.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It's a common Jewish name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "A red-haired man.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he was some sort of professor from the University of Brno, which was Leo's university.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And Leo knew him, and wouldn't go and work with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What Leo's reasons were, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he started stuffing this hernia in, and within about three or four minutes, the man was lying there normal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they bring out boxes of belts, and they have thousands of belts, you know, hernia belts.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they try this one and try that one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You've probably never seen a hernia belt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Have you seen a hernia belt?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You now, they are made with this special steel which is bent and sprung to fit your body.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So all the belts that they were trying on this man were loose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you can't bend it, because there's no heat, you know, to-- to temper steel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's no way of bending it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they tried to bend it, but it's spring steel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's-- it's not possible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Mengele says to the doctor, send him tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he writes on a piece of paper a prescription that I should bring small hernia belts.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That you should bring?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
